      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad Bin Abu Nasr, from Hammad Bin Usman, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The (grape) juice is not Prohibited until it boils’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from ibn abu Nasr from Hammad ibn ‘Uthaman who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘Juice (grape juice) is not unlawful until it boils.’” "
        ]
      }
